{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1673950149.9973874", "card_id": "Q_579202124", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 847}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国家统计局发布 2022 全年经济数据，GDP 同比增长 3.0％，这一数据透露了哪些信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "初步核算，全年国内生产总值 1210207 亿元，按不变价格计算，比上年增长 3.0%。分产业看，第一产业增加值 88345 亿元比上年增长 4.1%；第二产业增加值 483164 亿元，增长 3.8%；第三产业增加值 638698 亿元，增长 2.3%。分季度看，一季度国内生产总值同比增长 4.8%，二季度增长 0.4%，三季度增长 3.9%，四季度增长 2.9%。从环比看，四季度国内生产总值与三季度持平。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-38dd9031013c55a3852a3cad1f95ba0e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1125 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579202124"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyajC4LiFxtIfEAMaCDkwOTkzMTU0IKqCmJ4GMDQ4rRJAAHIJNTc5MjAyMTI0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1673950149.9983082", "card_id": "Q_579220044", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 621}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "暴雪中国发布更新说明，「与网易顺延谈判失败、 23 日将中止国服游戏服务」，有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "1 月 17 日，暴雪中国发布对国服玩家社区的更新说明，内容如下："}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-68a8c12dce7add8d6a922bc27004cc8b_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1062 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579220044"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyajC4LiFxtIfEAMaCDkwOTk3MTUwIP/emJ4GMB44kgdAAXIJNTc5MjIwMDQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1673950149.999011", "card_id": "Q_579034254", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 188}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「围炉煮茶」已致多地多人中毒，目前各地情况如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，围炉煮茶、围炉烧烤成了颇受欢迎的「网红」社交形式。然而，温馨场景下也暗藏危险，多地多人因「围炉」导致的一氧化碳中毒送医。「围炉煮茶」已致多地多人中毒"}, "image_area": {"